esqlQuery.esql:
// Alert when pod CPU usage exceeds 95% of its limit.
//
// What triggers this alert:
// Pod CPU usage above 95% of configured limit — throttling imminent.
//
// Action needed:
// Increase CPU limits, optimize workload, or scale horizontally.
//
// Adjust threshold as needed (e.g., 0.9 for 90% early warning).
TS metrics-kubernetes.pod-*
| WHERE `kubernetes.pod.cpu.usage.limit.pct` > 0.95
| STATS doc_count = COUNT(*)
  BY `orchestrator.cluster.name`, `kubernetes.pod.name`, `kubernetes.namespace`
| WHERE doc_count > 0
